Processes the incoming log entry and displays it by means of the native logging capabilities of the client.

Supported browsers: * Firefox <4 using FireBug (if available). * Firefox >=4 using the Web Console. * WebKit browsers using the Web Inspector/Developer Tools. * Internet Explorer 8+ using the F12 Developer Tools. * Opera >=10.60 using either the Error Console or Dragonfly

Currently unsupported browsers: * Opera <10.60
